The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) at the weekend announced the change of date for the screening of aspirants for the governorship ticket in the Osun State Governorship from the scheduled date of Tuesday, January 11, 2022, to a new date of Wednesday, January 12, 2022.
The PDP maintained that the venue for the screening is still the PDP National Secretariat, Abuja, at 10.00am.Aspirants cleared at the screening will contest the election primary for the PDP ticket.
The PDP expressing regrets for any inconveniences the change in date may have caused members, stated: “all aspirants, leaders, critical stakeholders and members of our party in Osun State should take note and by this, guided accordingly.”
